        "TileImage": "$($repository e5cd7d51-fa8f-42fb-93de-c885b45a0925).Image",
        "Description": "An alternative assassin has been selected for this mission to assassinate Eric Soders, but the assassin is new to this line of work, and has requested for a handful of targets to be taken care of before they feel comfortable taking a chance. A guard which they&apos;re afraid of, a nurse they fear being spotted by, a pilot who gave them an odd look, and, of course, the chief surgeon. I know it sounds cowardly, Agent 47, and that&apos;s because it is. However, they are silent and quick, so we must assist.",
